## Per-Agent Notes
Lena: Plain English always. Short paragraphs. Approachable, not academic.
Rio: LinkedIn Ads primary. Professional targeting. Exclude wealth management segments.
Atlas: Clean, modern. Light or dark theme. App UI screenshots preferred. Data viz elements welcome.
Kai: LinkedIn is primary platform (professional + fintech audience). Watch session frequency for churn.
Felix: SaaS model. LTV:CAC > 3:1 always. Track MRR, expansion MRR, contraction MRR separately.